Key Match Events: David Wiese hit 13 runs off 4 balls in the super over to help Namibia win
Ruben Trumpelmann took 4 wickets, including 2 with his first two balls, in Namibia's victory
Miscellaneous Highlights: This was Namibia's third appearance in the T20 World Cup
Others: Namibia's run-chase faltered after a stunning bowling performance by Oman's Mehran Khan
Jan Frylinck was the top-scorer for Namibia with 45 runs
Mehran Khan was sensational with ball in hand, giving his side a shot at super over victory with figures of 3/7 in his three overs
